rs.fromIssuerLocation to perform live OIDC discovery and a\nJWKS fetch of https://www.googleapis.com/oauth2/v3/certs on every CI\nrun. Any egress blip failed the build (RemoteKeySourceException).\n\nRewrite the test to run fully offline using the existing local RSA\nfixtures: testExpiredToken now mints a locally-signed token with a\nfixed past exp and asserts the actual expiry error, and a new\ntestUnknownSigningKey preserves the original intent (token signed\nwith a key/algorithm the server does not accept) by signing with\nRS384 against the RS256 decoder, asserting the same error message the\nold test relied on Google's key rotation to produce. The unused\nGoogle token, client id and provider setup are removed. Test-only\nchange; no production code affected.","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"c0ca4f68c9bbdb1304369ed805102fc646ae9f41","tree_id":"d6f1385cc842a9b942d3c72f4c34e54c8506a5e1","timestamp":"2026-07-17T16:37:51Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis